      • createProcessList

        protected static de.esoco.data.element.DataElementList createProcessList(java.lang.String sName,
                                                                         java.util.Collection<java.lang.Class<? extends de.esoco.process.ProcessDefinition>> rProcessClasses,
                                                                         java.util.Collection<java.lang.Class<? extends de.esoco.process.ProcessDefinition>> rAllowedProcesses)
        Converts an array of ProcessDefinition classes into a data element list that contains instances of ProcessDescription entries. PROCESS_SEPARATOR entries will be mapped to a list separator process description.
        Parameters:
        sName - The name of the returned data element list
        rProcessClasses - The array of process classes to convert
        rAllowedProcesses - The allowed processes for the current user
        Returns:
        The list of process descriptions
